PRELIMINARY LICENSE NOTICE -- DAY 0
====================================

This repository is the day-0 planning anchor for Yujin Pilot.
Source code shipped here today (this LICENSE, README.md,
docs/SPEC.md, CLAUDE.md) is published under the Apache License,
Version 2.0.

When Yujin Pilot ships its commercial features (desktop binary,
voice pipeline, macros engine, conflict resolver, license-gated
peer dispatch beyond the trial limits), those features will
ship under a separate COMMERCIAL LICENSE issued by Yujin
(rpaforce.com) on a per-seat or per-organisation basis.

The MCP discovery layer's WIRE PROTOCOL stays open and is
documented as part of the NAC v2.3 spec, so any tool can
implement compatible discovery.

